              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                class="defaultlink pad"
                align="center"
                valign="top"
                style="
                  font-family: Poppins, Arial, sans-serif;
                  color: #000000;
                  font-size: 13px;
                  line-height: 18px;
                  padding: 25px;
                "
              >
                Hi <strong><%= data.firstname %></strong>,<br /><br />

                Exciting news! You’ve won <%= data.raffleData.raffle_name %>!<br /><br />
