                &bull; You will receive your prize from <%= data.businessName %>
                within 14 days<br /><br />

                &bull; Share the good news to your socials and be sure to tag
                us!<br /><br />

                &bull; Check the [WINNERS PAGE]!<br /><br />
                &bull; Please let us know when you receive your prize!<br /><br />
                Thank you for participating with Raffily, we hope you enjoy your
                amazing prize!<br /><br />
                [WINNERS PAGE]<br /><br />

                If you have any questions or need further assistance, don’t
                hesitate to reach out. Stay tuned for more exciting raffles in
                the future — you might be lucky again!<br />
                Raffily<br /><br />

                Check out our live raffles now!<br /><br />
                EXPLORE RAFFLES
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td bgcolor="#110044" style="padding: 25px 25px" class="pad">
                <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      class="defaultlink"
                      align="center"
                      valign="top"
                      style="
                        font-family: Poppins, Arial, sans-serif;
                        color: #ffffff;
                        font-size: 14px;
                        line-height: 21px;
                        padding: 0px 0px 16px 0px;
                        font-weight: bold;
                      "
                    >
                      Let's Get Social
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td width="32" style="width: 32px" valign="middle">
                      <a
                        href="https://www.tiktok.com/@raffilyuk?_t=8qj3YTsxLOK&_r=1"
                        target="_blank"
                        ><img
                          src="https://raffily.com/email_images/tiktok.png"
                          width="32"
                          style="display: block; max-width: 32px"
                          border="0"
                      /></a>
                    </td>
                    <td width="24" style="width: 24px">&nbsp;</td>
                    <td width="32" style="width: 32px" valign="middle">
                      <a
                        href="https://www.facebook.com/p/Raffily-61556451772407/"
                        target="_blank"
                        ><img
                          src="https://www.raffily.com/email_images/facebook.png"
                          width="32"
                          style="display: block; max-width: 32px"
                          border="0"
                      /></a>
                    </td>
                    <td width="24" style="width: 24px">&nbsp;</td>
                    <td width="32" style="width: 32px" valign="middle">
                      <a
                        href="https://www.instagram.com/raffilyuk/"
                        target="_blank"
                        ><img
                          src="https://www.raffily.com/email_images/instagram.png"
                          width="32"
                          style="display: block; max-width: 32px"
                          border="0"
                      /></a>
                    </td>
                    <td width="24" style="width: 24px">&nbsp;</td>
                    <td width="32" style="width: 32px" valign="middle">
                      <a href="https://x.com/RaffilyUK" target="_blank"
                        ><img
                          src="https://www.raffily.com/email_images/twitter.png"
                          width="32"
                          style="display: block; max-width: 32px"
                          border="0"
                      /></a>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                class="defaultlink pad"
                align="center"
                valign="top"
                style="
                  font-family: Poppins, Arial, sans-serif;
                  color: #000000;
                  font-size: 13px;
                  line-height: 21px;
                  padding: 25px;
                "
